{"tid":29274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱行街有人問我借錢","createTime":"2016-12-08T12:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T12:56:10.000Z","uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"714158f877d09642ef6bfe2b62fb99196f2daf57","tid":29274,"uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"手上拎住張啲字化晒又勁皺嘅紙<br />\n走過嚟話唔見銀包 <br />\n啱啱去咗報失<br />\n問我借十蚊廿蚊<br />\n搭車番天水圍<br />\n我屌佢老母附近撚有警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做戲都做好啲啦<br />\nbtw見佢咁撚可憐<br />\n要喺條街到呃錢<br />\n最後畀咗10蚊佢 <br />\n點知佢多謝都冇句<br />\n仲想攞多幾蚊 <br />\n下次再有人問我借錢<br />\n我一定唔撚借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2ac59b9bc89a068ed89750a6a7f73e52611b8f","tid":29274,"uid":378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"你比得錢就已經輸左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409a6b156a44e31795b5702852253c78a155bf4c","tid":29274,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"你試吓同佢講你陪佢去輕鐵話買飛<br />\n你睇吓佢會唔會多謝你"}]}